  "reference_number": "CYB0074",
  "remarks": "\nArtem Valeryvich OCHICHENKO is or has been an involved person in relevant cyber activity commissioned by GRU Unit 74455. In this capacity, Artem Valeryvich OCHICHENKO is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting the commission, planning or preparation of relevant cyber activity. Such activity that Artem Valeryvich OCHICHENKO is or has been involved in undermines, or is intended to undermine, the integrity, propsperity or security of the United Kingdom or a country other than the United Kingdom.\n",
